Shareable is an award-winning nonprofit news, action and connection hub for the sharing economy transformation. Sharing Cities Network, run by Shareable, connects local sharing activists in cities around the world for as a form of mutual support and movement building. They have produced several reports and proposals for new policies and institutional structures to harness the potential fo the sharing economy revolution.

